(31, 189, 'Rizki Tunjung Sari', 'rizki', '<div class="uk-width-medium-1">\r\n<div class="uk-grid">\r\n<div class="uk-width-large-2-10 uk-width-medium-3-10 uk-width-1-1 uk-float-left uk-text-center"><img class="uk-margin-bottom tm-image-round uk-thumbnail" src="images/profile/kiki.jpg" alt="CCO Image" width="233" height="232" /></div>\r\n<div class="uk-width-large-8-10 uk-width-medium-7-10 uk-width-1-1 uk-text-center-small">\r\n<p class="tm-primary-color uk-text-large">AX Developer Staff</p>\r\n<p><i> Kiki was born at Magelang, September 19th 1991. She graduated from Science and Technology Faculty, UIN Sunan Kalijaga Yogyakarta, majoring Informatics (2009-2013).</i></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p><i> In 2011 she worked as web developer at Bin Tolchah Tour Travel Kalasan. In 2012 she worked as lab assistant for Information System at Science and Technology Intergrated Laboratory. She also worked as English tentor for junior high-school and C++ tentor from 2011 to 2012 at Yogyakarta. She worked as warehouse staff at PT BAM Temanggung from 2013 to 2014. And now shes working at CV Lidah Buaya Group Magelang as IT Application staff (AX developer) from 2014. <br /><br />  She built a website for tour travel company to online reservation using PHP and MySQL. At the end of her study, she built a software to recognize the ripeness of tomatoes using MATLAB and JAVA EE. Before became AX developer, she focused at Delphi and SQL Server to build desktop applications. Now, shes working as AX Developer and doing customization within AX include creating forms and reports using X++ and Visual Studio 2010. Interest of Programming : AX, X++, Visual Studio, Delphi. Interest of Database : SQL Server </i></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 10, '2015-05-20 07:02:06', 416, '', '2015-05-23 23:37:36', 416, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-05-20 07:02:06', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"none","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"none