(36, 194, 'Twosilo', 'twosilo', '<div class="uk-width-medium-1-2">\r\n<div class="uk-grid">\r\n<div class="uk-width-large-2-10 uk-width-medium-3-10 uk-width-1-1 uk-float-left uk-text-center"><img class="uk-margin-bottom tm-image-round uk-thumbnail" src="images/profile/twosilo.jpg" alt="CCO Image" width="233" height="232" /></div>\r\n<div class="uk-width-large-8-10 uk-width-medium-7-10 uk-width-1-1 uk-text-center-small">\r\n<p class="tm-primary-color uk-text-large">DBA &amp; Analyst Support Staff</p>\r\n<p><i>- Twosilo Nugroho was born in Boyolali on August 13, 1990. The graduates of SMK N 2 Temanggung Department of Computer Engineering and Networks (TKJ) in 2008.<br /><br /> - Previously worked for one half years in GANESHA COMPUTER in Bekasi as one of the hardware and network technician.<br /><br /> - And then in 2011 worked in cooperation of Semarak Dana Temanggung as a Debt Collector for Ambarawa and the surrounding area.<br /><br /> - In 2012 I worked in Kayu Lima Utama Temanggung as a production operator in the Assembling Department. During work on Kayu Lima Utama, I also opened my own business under the name of TN Computer that work in the servicing and installation of computers , and also services in script typing .</i></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p><i>- And then I worked in the Company Barokah Agawe Makmur (BAM) which is engaged in the manufacture of plywood where I play a role in the production operator .<br /><br /> - Join Lidah Buaya Group in August 2014 as IT support. In the month of January 2015 switched position as IT Networking who are responsible in terms of network troubleshooting, cctv, etc.</i></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 7, '2015-05-20 07:18:38', 416, '', '2015-05-23 03:57:37', 416, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-05-20 07:18:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"none","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"none","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":fal