(40, 198, 'Raditya Dimas', 'radit', '<div class="uk-width-medium-1">\r\n<div class="uk-grid">\r\n<div class="uk-width-large-2-10 uk-width-medium-3-10 uk-width-1-1 uk-float-left uk-text-center"><img class="uk-margin-bottom tm-image-round uk-thumbnail" src="images/profile/dimas1.jpg" alt="CCO Image" width="233" height="232" /></div>\r\n<div class="uk-width-large-8-10 uk-width-medium-7-10 uk-width-1-1 uk-text-center-small">\r\n<p class="tm-primary-color uk-text-large">Helpdesk &amp; User Support Staff</p>\r\n<p><i> Dimas satria gilar sandi mahardika or commonly called radit born 3 August 1990. Born as the eldest of three brothers in the village Kalimas randudongkal districts, a village that is MEWAH "Mepet Sawah" and beautiful, with the majority of handsome and beautiful as well.</i></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p><i> Basic education which is taken from the SD Negri 3 Kalimas randudongkal, SD Negri 2 Kebondalem pemalang, SMP Negri 2 Randudongkal, SMK Texmaco Pemalang, then continued in the University Amikom Yogyakarta.<br /><br />  When junior dimas became active in organizational activities, exschool, up to the time the class 2 SMK dimas designated as Paskibraka (heritage flag raisers forces) troops 45 district level in 2007-2008. <br /><br />  dimas entering university started a business designing berbasi blog PHP and Java with google adsense earnings through the profit rata2 $ 100 per month, after the business starts running and growing again with the creation of an online streaming radio, as it is mounted at the university Tidar magelang. <br /><br />  amikom graduated from university in 2012 dimas worked in various large companies like, AD! Java partnership as Web programmers, PT Valbury as Financial Consultant, PT Eka tirta as standalone IT Support and the last at PT Aloe Vera Group as an IT Helpdesk that plays an important role in all operations in the company concerned. <br /><br />  In this life I should have a principle of life that is with me always trying and always prayed to realize the ideals that I want, I''m sure, and always optimistic that behind this all GOD Almighty had other plans. then try and trust. </i></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 7, '2015-05-20 07:22:11', 416, '', '2015-05-23 23:47:14', 416, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-05-20 07:22:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"none","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"none","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 4, 3, '', '', 1, 24, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 1, '*', ''),
(41, 199, 'Dimas Ragil', 'ragil', '<div class="uk-width-medium-1-2">\r\n<div class="uk-grid">\r\n<div class="uk-width-large-2-10 uk-width-medium-3-10 uk-width-1-1 uk-float-left uk-text-center"><img class="uk-margin-bottom tm-image-round uk-thumbnail" src="images/profile/dimas2.jpg" alt="CCO Image" width="233" height="232" /></div>\r\n<div class="uk-width-large-8-10 uk-width-medium-7-10 uk-width-1-1 uk-text-center-small">\r\n<p class="tm-primary-color uk-text-large">Helpdesk &amp; User Support Staff</p>\r\n<p><i>Dimas was born in Jakarta, july 16, 1988. The graduates of SMK Muhammadiyah Payaman Automotive Engineering Education in 2007 .</i></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p><i> after graduating, in 2008 imigrated to Borneo to try to gain experience and work in there. because there is not in line with expectations, then I go home to Magelang and try to continue education in faculty. 2009 I registered as students at the University Muhammadiyah Magelang. Faculty of Informatics.<br /><br /> While studying at the University Muhammadiyah Magelang, has a small business that delivery services and installation of computer and network named "AER Comp" and serves as one of the technicians. in addition to my work at AER comp, I also worked as administrator, operators and technicians in internet cafes named "Sandi Net"<br /><br /> began to join with CV. Lidah Buaya Group on 4 Agustus 2014. The first work in CV. Lidah Buaya Group be accepted as IT shopfloor . Than move in IT operation on 1 Februari 2015. On IT operation handling eror hardware and system operation or commonly spelled IT helpdesk .</i></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 7, '2015-05-20 07:23:00', 416, '', '2015-05-26 01:46:51', 416, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-05-20 07:23:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"none","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"none","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","u