(104, 153, 'Home Team', '', '<p><img class="uk-align-center" src="images/yootheme/demo/default/home_worldmap.png" alt="Demo" width="980" height="390" /></p>\r\n<h1 class="tm-negativ-margin-top uk-text-center">Our Team</h1>\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;"><i>We work with passion to deliver each projects with the best quality. We are some very enthusiastic people. Thus, let us introduce ourselves.</i></h2>\r\n<hr class="uk-grid-divider" />\r\n<div class="uk-grid">\r\n<div class="uk-width-medium-1-2">\r\n<div class="uk-grid">\r\n<div class="uk-width-large-2-10 uk-width-medium-3-10 uk-width-1-1 uk-text-center"><img class="uk-margin-bottom tm-image-round uk-thumbnail" src="images/profile/ovan.png" alt="CEO Image" /></div>\r\n<div class="uk-width-large-8-10 uk-width-medium-7-10 uk-width-1-1 uk-text-center-small">\r\n<p class="tm-primary-color uk-text-large"><a href="index.php/profil/ict-head-division">Ovan Diana</a></p>\r\n<p class="uk-text-bold">ICT Head Division</p>\r\n<p><i>Ovan Diana graduated form the Economic Faculty of Airlangga University, Surabaya majoring in Accounting in 2002 and Teknik Informatika of STIKI, Malang majoring in Sistem Informasi in 2006...</i></p>\r\n<p class="tm-primary-color uk-text-large"></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="uk-width-medium-1-2">\r\n<div class="uk-grid">\r\n<div class="uk-width-large-2-10 uk-width-medium-3-10 uk-width-1-1 uk-float-left uk-text-center"><img class="uk-margin-bottom tm-image-round uk-thumbnail" src="images/profile/yusep.jpg" alt="CCO Image" width="233" height="232" /></div>\r\n<div class="uk-width-large-8-10 uk-width-medium-7-10 uk-width-1-1 uk-text-center-small">\r\n<p class="tm-primary-color uk-text-large"><a href="index.php/bussines-system/yusep-inang">Yusep Inang</a></p>\r\n<p class="uk-text-bold">Bussines System Dept. Head</p>\r\n<p><i>My name Yusep Inang, I graduated from high school in 2003 managemant informatics and computer Bandung (STMIK) I began to join in LidahBuaay Group March 2004, m